snippet.title: Impulse - Development Update #1
snippet.description:
This is a long form development update video to keep you up-to-date with everything happening behind the scenes here at Ascendance Games. Watch the continuing development for Impulse by following us on social media, and joining our Discord!

Impulse is now available, download today! 
https://ascendancegames.com/download.html

This is Impulse. A play-for-free, play-to-earn first-person multiplayer shooter by Ascendance Games. Play for free and collect rare items and DNA, or amp it up a bit and play in our Credit Arena where every kill is worth money. Everyone from the new players, the pros, and all of the unsung heroes of the world can make their mark in our game permanently. Play by yourself or join together with your friends in this first-of-it’s-kind play-to-earn shooter where we bring esports to everyone!

Get an Impulse Founder’s Pack today: 
http://www.ascendancegames.com/

Follow us on our socials!
Discord: https://cutt.ly/ImpulseDiscord
Twitter: https://cutt.ly/ImpulseTwitter
Reddit: https://cutt.ly/ImpulseReddit
Twitch: https://cutt.ly/ImpulseTwitch
TikTok: https://cutt.ly/ImpulseTikTok
Instagram: https://cutt.ly/ImpulseInstagram
Facebook: https://cutt.ly/ImpulseFacebook
Telegram: https://cutt.ly/ImpulseTelegram

Subscribe to see more trailers and development update videos: 
https://cutt.ly/ImpulseYTSubscribe

#Impulse #AscendanceGames #FPS #PlayToEarn #FreeToPlay
